graph TD
    User((Creator/Freelancer)) -->|Upload Request| API[API Gateway]
    API -->|Pre-signed URL| S3_Raw[(S3 Raw Assets)]
    User -->|Direct Upload| S3_Raw
    
    S3_Raw -->|Event Trigger| SNS[SNS/EventBridge]
    SNS -->|Queue Message| SQS[Processing Queue]
    
    subgraph "Processing Cluster"
        WorkerMgr[Task Orchestrator]
        W1[Image AI Worker]
        W2[Video/Audio Worker]
        W3[Embedding Worker]
    end
    
    SQS --> WorkerMgr
    WorkerMgr --> W1
    WorkerMgr --> W2
    WorkerMgr --> W3
    
    W1 & W2 & W3 --> DB[(PostgreSQL + pgvector)]
    W3 --> VectorDB[(Pinecone/Milvus)]
    
    W1 & W2 --> S3_Proc[(S3 Processed/Proxies)]
    
    DB --> API
    API -->|Real-time Updates| User